stories.description: The Mosque Admin adds a new inventory item to the system to keep track of stock levels. This ensures accurate inventory management.
stories.expected_outcome:
New inventory item is added and visible in the inventory list.

VALIDATION: Assert: New item 'Peci' appears in inventory list with quantity '100'.

steps.target: Step 10: Verify new item is listed in inventory

stories.description: The Super Admin searches for inventory items supplied by a specific vendor to review stock levels and vendor performance.
stories.expected_outcome:
Inventory list displays only items supplied by 'aifamart'.

VALIDATION: Assert: Inventory table shows only items with 'Nama Vendor' as 'aifamart'.

steps.target: Step 3: Verify inventory list shows only 'aifamart' items

stories.description: The Ministry Admin filters inactive inventory items and activates them to ensure they are available for use.
stories.expected_outcome:
Selected inactive inventory item is activated and status changes to 'Active'.

VALIDATION: Assert: Status of item changes to 'Active' in inventory list.

steps.target: Step 1: Click 'more_vert' on an inactive item
Step 3: Verify item status changes to 'Active'

stories.description: The Mosque Admin uploads an image for an inventory item to provide visual reference for stock items.
stories.expected_outcome:
Image is uploaded and displayed with the inventory item.

VALIDATION: Assert: Image thumbnail appears next to the inventory item in the list.

steps.target: Step 4: Verify image is displayed with item

stories.user_persona: Mosque Admin cancelling an inventory addition
stories.description: The Mosque Admin starts to add a new inventory item but decides to cancel the action to avoid errors.
stories.expected_outcome:
Inventory addition is canceled and no new item is added.

VALIDATION: Assert: No new item appears in inventory list.

steps.target: Step 4: Verify no new item is added
